    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's all gone. years of work, every paper, every theory... it was all based on a systematic error i missed. i'm not just a failure, i'm a fraud. there's no coming back from this. i look at my life and i just see a massive, empty void where a purpose used to be. i don't even recognize the person in the mirror anymore.",
