    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "\"start over\"... how? there's no \"starting over\" when there's nothing left to build on. the person i was, the person i spent my whole life becoming, is just... gone. it's like the person who did all that work never even existed. it feels more like there's just nothing there at all. just a weight that won't stop pulling me down.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
